<br />
The LDS Church acknowledged<sup id="cite_ref-LDS-JST-ackn_10-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-LDS-JST-ackn-10">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> on their website that "<span style="color:gray">[as]</span> <span style="color:gray">[Joseph Smith]</span> worked on these changes <span style="color:gray">[to the JST]</span>, he appears in many instances to have consulted respected commentaries by biblical scholars, studying them out in his mind as a part of the revelatory process."<sup id="cite_ref-LDS-JST-ackn_10-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-LDS-JST-ackn-10">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></span>
</li>
